  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this retrospective and prospective study, the aim is to determine a score for predicting a
      fibrinogen &lt;1.5g/L (corresponding to European threshold of Directors recommendations of
      fibrinogen concentrates)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
